message: Initial commit from Create Next App
feat: add basic ui
feat: finish basic functions
feat: add stream support
feat: add settings ui
feat: add dark theme support
feat: update style and timeout handler
feat: add analytics
feat: support code highlight and markdown gfm
feat: add check update
fix: #23 errors when dev on windows

feat: #2 add access control by
access code
feat: #27 add docker image publish actions
feat: #2 add prompt list
feat: #2 add prompt hints
feat: add lint-staged
chore: move some dependencies to devDependencies
feat: import ramarkBreaks plugin

app: polyfill Array.at

This fixes compatibility issue with older browsers like WeChat webview.
The summary feature now works as expected.
fix: #244 optimize polyfill
fix: #289 use highlight.js instead of prism
fix: #397 #373 Array.prototype.at polyfill errors
doc: update document
chore(deps): introduce dnd

Merge pull request #509 from xiaotianxt/feat/dnd-xiaotianxt

Drag & Drop support for ChatList
feat: close #118 add stop all button
fix: #832 update nextjs version to 13.3.0
fix: error in windows
refactor: close #643 use react router
feat: close #951 support mermaid
refactor: llm client api
refactor: #1000 #1179 api layer for client-side only mode and local models
chore: upgrade nextjs to 13.4.2
fix: #1498 missing text caused by streaming
feat: wont fetch prompts in every building
fix: #1612 infinite loading
feat: close #580 export messages as image
feat: #1000 client-side only and desktop app
fixup
fix: #1954 lazy render bugs
feat: add app dev mode

feat: add app logo and
release workflow
feat: enable drag area for tauri apps
Resolves found vuln CVE-2023-2251
